data.Name: Lil Dicky
data.Bio: Lil Dicky (or LD) (born David Andrew Burd on 15 March 1988) is an American rapper and comedian. He came to prominence with the release of the music video of his song "Ex-Boyfriend", which went viral with more than one million views on YouTube in 24 hours. He released his debut album Professional Rapper on July 31, 2015. In 2018, his song "Freaky Friday", featuring Chris Brown, became a worldwide hit.
